OL,3,CD-Day veteran awarded British Empire
OL,4,CMedal says Britain today is
OL,5,C'disappointing'
OL,7,FHe was later stationed near Bergen-
OL,8,FBelsen when the camp was liberated by
OL,9,FBritish troops in April 1945.
OL,11,FMr Kersh said he tells schoolchildren
OL,12,Fduring his talks about how the
OL,13,Fconflict began, adding: "There'd be no
OL,14,Fneed for a war now, we've got the
OL,15,Fwrong attitude."
OL,17,FThe veteran said he "absolutely" sees
OL,18,Fcomparisons between now and the period
OL,19,Fjust before the Second World War,
OL,20,Fadding that Russia is "threatening the
OL,21,Fwest."
