OL,3,CD-Day veteran awarded British Empire
OL,4,CMedal says Britain today is
OL,5,C'disappointing'
OL,7,FHe went on: "The top budget should be
OL,8,Fdefence, there's nothing there for
OL,9,Fanything else. That's all there is.
OL,11,F"Defence must come first, second,
OL,12,Fthird, fourth and fifth, because only
OL,13,Fif you're strong, you won't be
OL,14,Fattacked."
OL,16,FMr Kersh compared today's Western
OL,17,Fleaders to Neville Chamberlain, whose
OL,18,F1930s appeasement of Hitler failed,
OL,19,Fsaying: "They think they've just got
OL,20,Fto hope and make speeches."
